CNCP v1 23419
{
  "concept": "vuejs/core#5980: The result of ShallowReadonly() on a reactive object can't be spreaded on some iOS device",
  "version": "1.0",
  "created_at": "2026-03-15T04:26:12.939319+00:00",
  "text": "The result of ShallowReadonly() on a reactive object can't be spreaded on some iOS device\n\n### Vue version\n\n3.2.34\n\n### Link to minimal reproduction\n\nhttps://codesandbox.io/s/vuejs-ios-props-shallowreadonly-issue-lkksug?file=/src/App.vue\n\n### Steps to reproduce\n\n```typescript\r\nimport { reactive, shallowReadonly } from 'vue';\r\n\r\nconst foo = reactive({\r\n    a: 1,\r\n});\r\n\r\nconst spreadedFoo = {\r\n    ...foo,\r\n};\r\n\r\nconst spreadedBar = { ...shallowReadonly(foo) };\r\n// results are not same on some iOS device (eg. iOS 12.5 / iOS 11.3)\r\nconsole.log(spreadedFoo, spreadedBar);\r\n```\r\n\n\n### What is expected?\n\nThese results are same.\n\n### What is actually happening?\n\nresults are not same on iOS device below iOS 12.5\r\nUnexpected results:\r\niOS 12.5 / iOS 11.3\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/8327041/169679953-1dffebfc-d328-4402-84fd-21515413d688.png)\r\n\r\nexpected results:\r\nChrome 100\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/8327041/169679982-d8f238d4-4dc5-4b75-ac7e-7d9e272c833a.png)\r\niOS 15.3\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/8327041/169680080-05ec620b-62f4-46bc-81b4-407118197922.png)\n\n### System Info\n\n```shell\nThis issues can be reproduced on iOS 12.5 / iOS 11.3.\r\niOS 15.3 / Chrome 100 is expected result.\n```\n\n\n### Any additional comments?\n\nNo.",
  "language": "en",
  "keywords": [
    "browser specific",
    "🔩 p2-edge-case"
  ],
